Simple Ass Runner - SAR
=======================
A tiny task runner

Usage
-----
$ sar
• build
• run
• test

$ sar build

After running "sar build" it executes the command under build section in your sarc

Features
--------
running commands by name
thats it. nothing more

Installing
----------
go install github.com/jvqtil/sar@latest
or download a binary from releases

Syntax
------
sar uses Makefile format:

name:
	command
